Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝！
